name: Bulldog Billionaires
description: BONE is the bulldog's lifeline and is the utility token for Solana NFT Project "Bulldog Billionaires". The token is essential for doghouses, auctions/raffles, bulldog upgrades, title claims/breeding, and much more. BONE token is deflationary meaning, BONE spent is BONE burned. BONE can only be retrieved by staking a Bulldog Billionaires NFT.
